         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Modular Unit — Lease Buy Out</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>17/2416</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="44211000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SUPPLIES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Cardiff and Vale University Health Board wish to inform the market that they intend to purchase an existing modular building which is sited on the University of Wales site.</P>
               <P>The Modular build consists of 6 No Portakabin ultima UK 123 modules and 1 No portakabin portaloo PL062K.</P>
               <P>The Health Board are looking to purchase the facility as the cost to remove the modular building including disconnections and reinstatement of the site was not economically viable when the unit could be utilised for medical services.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">131200</VAL_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="44211100"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKL22"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>University Hospital of Wales, Cardiff</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Cardiff and Vale University Health Board wish to inform the market that they intend to purchase an existing modular building which is sited on the University of Wales site.</P>
                  <P>The Modular build consists of 6 No Portakabin ultima UK 123 modules and 1 No portakabin portaloo PL062K.</P>
                  <P>The Health Board are looking to purchase the facility as the cost to remove the modular building including disconnections and reinstatement of the site was not economically viable when the unit could be utilised for medical services.</P>
                  <P>A similar unit could not be provided by another provider for a comparable cost taking into consideration the cost of removal and reinstatement and purchase.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
         <PROCEDURE>
            <DIRECTIVE_2014_24_EU>
               <PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
                  <D_OUTSIDE_SCOPE/>
                  <D_JUSTIFICATION>
                     <P>The modular unit that the Health Board wishes to purchase is currently situated on the University of Wales, Heath Site. The existing unit was leased under a joint working agreement with a key supplier to the Health Board however given the ongoing financial pressures it was requested that the lease was terminated.</P>
                     <P>The cost of removal and reinstatement of the unit was not commercially viable, therefore the UHB requested a purchase price for the existing unit. Purchasing the unit not only provides an option that is more financially viable but would support with the ongoing accommodation pressures.</P>
                     <P>A similar unit could not be provided by another provider for a comparable cost taking into consideration the cost of removal and reinstatement and purchase.</P>
                  </D_JUSTIFICATION>
               </PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
            </DIRECTIVE_2014_24_EU>
